OL,3,CThames Water crisis worsens as parent
OL,4,Cfirm defaults on #400m loan
OL,6,FThames Water has seen its troubles
OL,7,Fworsen after its parent company told
OL,8,Fcreditors it has defaulted on some of
OL,9,Fits debts.
OL,11,FIt comes after Kemble Water Finance
OL,12,FLimited failed to meet a deadline to
OL,13,Fpay interest payments due on the
OL,14,Ffirm's debt.
OL,16,FThe water firm's financial struggles
OL,17,Fworsened last month when it said its
OL,18,Finvestors had pulled a #500 million
OL,19,Ffunding lifeline that was due to be
OL,20,Fpaid at the end of April.
