OL,3,CThames Water crisis worsens as parent
OL,4,Cfirm defaults on #400m loan
OL,6,FSome of that was understood to be
OL,7,Fearmarked to pay the loans owed by
OL,8,FKemble.
OL,10,FThames Waters' 16 million customers
OL,11,Fwill not be affected.
OL,13,FOn Friday, Kemble, which is entirely
OL,14,Ffunded through dividends received from
OL,15,FThames Water, sent a formal notice of
OL,16,Fdefault to the holders of around #400
OL,17,Fmillion of company bonds.
