OL,6,FIn the notice, it is requested that
OL,7,Fits lenders and note-holders take "no
OL,8,Fcreditor action" in order to "provide
OL,9,Fa stable platform while all options
OL,10,Fare explored with all key
OL,11,Fstakeholders".
OL,13,FKemble added: "The company expects
OL,14,Fthat it will be in a position to
OL,15,Fprovide a further update in the coming
OL,16,Fweeks."
