OL,3,CThames Water crisis worsens as parent
OL,4,Cfirm defaults on #400m loan
OL,6,FIt follows reports earlier this week
OL,7,Fof two Chinese state-owned banks and
OL,8,FDutch bank ING are among a group of
OL,9,Flenders who could play an important
OL,10,Frole in the stability of Thames Water.
OL,12,FIt is understood the banks are owed
OL,13,Faround #190 million from the loans
OL,14,Fgiven to Kemble, which are due to
OL,15,Fexpire at the end of the month.
OL,17,FThe deadline could be extended after
OL,18,FThames Water said it would not be able
OL,19,Fto repay it.
