OL,3,CThames Water crisis worsens as parent
OL,4,Cfirm defaults on #400m loan
OL,6,FING, Bank of China, Industrial and
OL,7,FCommercial Bank of China, and Allied
OL,8,FIrish Banks are among the lenders
OL,9,Fbehind the loan, according to new
OL,10,Finformation reported by Sky News and
OL,11,Fthe Financial Times.
OL,13,FIt means lenders could take a stake in
OL,14,FThames Water if the loan is not repaid
OL,15,Fand Kemble is in default, which would
OL,16,Fbe expected to result in a
OL,17,Frestructuring process.
